This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the segmentation of brain tumors from MRI scans. The use of deep learning models for segmentation also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of ensemble models and hyper-parameters also suggests that it could belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the mention of radiomic features suggests that it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
